          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_031_sideB_0.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "The entire codebase needs to be migrated.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_031_sideB_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "We need to migrate all the code.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_031_sideB_2.mp3"
        }
      ],
      "note": null
    },
    {
      "cardId": "dummy_032",
      "cardType": "flippable",
      "sideA": "Son los artefactos, los objetos, no son acciones.",
      "sideB": [
        {
          "text": "They are the artifacts, the objects, not actions.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_032_sideB_0.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "They're artifacts, objects, not actions.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_032_sideB_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "Those are the artifacts and objects, not the actions.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_032_sideB_2.mp3"
        }
      ],
      "note": null
    },
    {
      "cardId": "dummy_033",
      "cardType": "flippable",
      "sideA": "Gracias por ser paciente conmigo.",
      "sideB": [
        {
          "text": "Thank you for being patient with me.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_033_sideB_0.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "Thanks for your patience.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_033_sideB_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "I appreciate your patience with me.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_033_sideB_2.mp3"
        },
        {
          "text": "Thanks for being patient with me.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_033_sideB_3.mp3"
        }
      ],
      "note": null
    },
    {
      "cardId": "dummy_034",
      "cardType": "flippable",
      "sideA": "Para ser honesto. Pienso que esto está fuera de mi alcance.",
      "sideB": [
        {
          "text": "To be honest, I think this is out of my reach.",
          "audioSrc": "public/data/audio/dummy/dummy_034_sideB_0.mp3"
